title: 267. Andy, Vaughn & DJ CTI: Jen Psaki White House Exit, Zelenskyy Demotes 2 Generals & "Made In The Image Of God"
itunes:title: 267. Andy, Vaughn & DJ CTI: Jen Psaki White House Exit, Zelenskyy Demotes 2 Generals & "Made In The Image Of God"
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ are joined in the studio by the Pastor of disaster and co-host of The MFCEO Project, Vaughn Kohler. They discuss Jen Psaki planning to leave the White House this spring for MSNBC, Zelensky demoting 2 Ukrainian generals calling them traitors, and President Biden's comments about the transgender community.
